# Scratchpad / design notes that aren't part of the shipped library.
references/

# Upstream esphome MQTT source files copied into our shadow at module load
# time so ESPHome's resource discovery ships them into the build dir.
# Source of truth is the user's esphome venv; checked in only is our host
# backend (mqtt_backend_host.{cpp,h}).
